                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-53-18711120 t18711120-53-punishment-42"></join>Twelve Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">CLARK</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18711120-53-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
