                        <interp inst="t18711120-53-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He also</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>**† <hi rend="italic">to a former conviction at this Court in July</hi>, 1862, <hi rend="italic">and it was stated by Ackrill, T R</hi> 4, <hi rend="italic">
that the gentleman who was assaulted and robbed on that occasion afterwards died from the effects of the violence. <rs id="t18711120-53-punishment-43" type="punishmentDescription">
